# RedPulse Dashboard Environment
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Instructions:
# 1. Obtain a Google Maps JavaScript API Key from https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Ensure the "Maps JavaScript API" is ENABLED.
# 3. Ensure your Google Cloud Project has Billing linked (required for JS Maps).
# 4. Replace 'your_google_maps_api_key' below with your actual key.
# 5. Restart the 'npm run dev' process.

VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key

